Concentration of microparticles in snowfields of Greenland and Antarctica

Data for Exercise 7.87

Format

A data frame with 34 observations on the following 4 variables.

antarc
a numeric vector
greenld
a numeric vector
concent
a numeric vector
site
a numeric vector

References
